{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maroon is an interactive virtual STEM laboratory and experimentation environment that allows you to explore various experiments and phenomena in an immersive and engaging way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main laboratory room consists of different experiment stations and acts as a three-dimensional menu. Choose any experiment to start. Currently, Maroon supports experiments from the fields of electromagnetism, electrostatics, oscillation, waves, analytical chemistry, and algorithms.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Experiments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Among others, you can try out the following experiments from the fields of physics, chemistry, and computer science:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Coulomb's Law</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Falling Coil (Electromagnetism)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Faraday's Law</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Huygen's Principle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Point Wave</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pendulum</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Van de Graaff Balloon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Van de Graaff Generator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3D Motion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cathode Ray Tube</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Viscosimeter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Planetary System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Titration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Catalyst</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sorting Algorithms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">State Machines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pathfinding Algorithms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minimum Spanning Tree</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perlin Noise</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Virtual Reality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maroon is also available for VR. Choose an experiment from the vending mac